节目主持人和前任主持人分享了他们对特朗普胜利的想法</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/donald-trump-on-cusp-of-us-election-victory-entertainment-world-reacts-3809992">娱乐界的许多人物都对特朗普的胜利做出了反应</a>，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-opens-show-with-fighting-prayer-for-us-following-trumps-election-victory-3810453">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/its-a-war-on-women-billie-eilish-and-more-voice-fears-over-donald-trumps-stance-on-womens-rights-after-election-win-3810306">比利·埃里什</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cardi-b-says-this-is-why-some-of-yall-states-be-getting-hurricanes-in-swiflty-deleted-tweet-over-donald-trump-election-win-3810200">卡迪·B</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-white-shares-blistering-attack-on-donald-trump-america-will-get-whatever-this-wannabe-dictator-wants-to-enact-3810360">杰克·怀特</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/moby-shares-advice-following-donald-trumps-election-win-its-not-going-to-benefit-anybody-to-doomscroll-3810373">莫比</a>。</p><p>特朗普的选举胜利首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-days-american-idiot-performance-on-letterman-in-2004-re-uploaded-to-youtube-after-trumps-election-win-3810568">，绿日后的2004年《美国白痴》在“ Letterman”上的表演重新上传</a>。</p> ;
